shinkawa ltd (6274) Details


			Shinkawa Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the research, development, design, manufacture, sale, and after-sales service of semiconductor manufacturing equipment in Japan and internationally. It provides wire bonders, die bonders, flip chip bonders, etc., as well as discrete assemblers. The company was formerly known as Shinkawa Seisakusho Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Shinkawa Ltd. in February 1980. Shinkawa Ltd. was founded in 1959 and is headquartered in Musashimurayama, Japan.
  			

